' Layer chain (vertical stack)
ApplicationLayer "1" -[hidden]down- "1" PresentationLayer
PresentationLayer "1" -[hidden]down- "1" SessionLayer
SessionLayer "1" -[hidden]down- "1" TransportLayer
TransportLayer "1" -[hidden]down- "1" NetworkLayer
NetworkLayer "1" -[hidden]down- "1" DataLinkLayer
DataLinkLayer "1" -[hidden]down- "1" PhysicalLayer

' IProtocolLayer relationships
note right of IProtocolLayer
  **OSI 7-Layer Model**
  Layer 7: Application
  Layer 6: Presentation
  Layer 5: Session
  Layer 4: Transport
  Layer 3: Network
  Layer 2: Data Link
  Layer 1: Physical
  
  Data flows:
  - Upstream: Physical ? Application (receive)
  - Downstream: Application ? Physical (send)
end note

